OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 23 May to Mon 1 Jun
OL,6,FSaturday will be warm with some
OL,7,Fshowery weather and even a chance of
OL,8,Fthunderstorms in places. Then by
OL,9,FSunday and through Bank Holiday
OL,10,FMonday, warm and fair weather is
OL,11,Fexpected to prevail. Through the
OL,12,Ffollowing week, high pressure is
OL,13,Fexpected to broadly remain in place
OL,14,Ffor much of the UK, and fine weather
OL,15,Fis likely to continue for most of the
OL,16,Fcountry. There may be occasions where
OL,17,Flow pressure to the north may bring
OL,18,Fsome brief spells of rain across
OL,19,Fnorthern parts, but in general fair
OL,20,Fweather will dominate. Temperatures
OL,21,Fare expected to be above normal,
OL,22,Ffeeling very warm at times with light
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fwinds.
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
