OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 2 Jun to Tue 16 Jun
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to continue to
OL,7,Fbring fair weather for most at first.
OL,8,FRain and showers are still possible at
OL,9,Ftimes, mainly across Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fand Scotland. As we head towards mid-
OL,11,FJune, more mixed conditions are likely
OL,12,Fwith spells of rain and showers. Drier
OL,13,Fweather is expected between any bouts
OL,14,Fof wetter weather. These drier
OL,15,Finterludes will tend to last longer
OL,16,Facross the south and east of England.
OL,17,FTemperatures are most likely to be
OL,18,Fnear or slightly above average
OL,19,Foverall, with some warm or very warm
OL,20,Fweather possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
